elements.name: Verify the user can register with correct credentials

steps.name: user lands on "Asians User System" page
verify user is on "Sign in to your account" page
user clicks on register button
verify user is on "Register" page
user inputs random email on register page
user inputs password "12345" on register page
user inputs confirm password "12345" on register page
user clicks on "Register" button
verify the user is logged in
